<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>About Us - Metro Mesh</title>
    <style>
      body {
        font-family: "Roboto Condensed", sans-serif;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #e0f2f7, #d1c4e9);
        color: #333;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 800px;
        margin: 40px auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background: linear-gradient(
          to bottom right,
          rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.9),
          rgba(240, 240, 240, 0.9)
        );
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
        text-align: center;
        flex: 1;
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        width: 85% !important;
        padding-bottom: 60px;
      }

      h1 {
        color: #6a1b9a;
        margin-bottom: 15px;
        font-size: 2.5em;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      h2 {
        color: #4a148c;
        font-size: 1.8em;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 1.1em;
        color: #555;
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .button {
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #6a1b9a, #4a148c);
        color: #fff;
        padding: 15px 30px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        font-weight: 600;
        font-size: 1em;
        box-shadow: 0 6px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      }

      footer {
        text-align: center;
        margin-top: 40px;
        padding: 20px;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        color: #777;
      }

      @media (min-width: 768px) {
        .container {
          padding: 80px;
          margin: 80px auto;
        }

        h1 {
          font-size: 3em;
        }

        h2 {
          font-size: 2em;
        }

        p {
          font-size: 1.3em;
        }

        .button {
          padding: 18px 35px;
          font-size: 1.2em;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>About Metro Mesh</h1>
      <p>
        At Metro Mesh, we believe in the power of local businesses and the
        importance of community. Our mission is to connect local businesses with
        their customers through innovative solutions and seamless communication.
      </p>
      <h2>Our Vision</h2>
      <p>
        We envision a world where every local business thrives and grows by
        leveraging the power of technology and community support. Our WhatsApp
        bot is designed to make it easier for businesses to reach their
        customers and for customers to discover new and exciting local
        businesses.
      </p>
      <h2>Our Mission</h2>
      <p>
        Our mission is to empower local businesses by providing them with the
        tools and resources they need to succeed. We are committed to fostering
        a strong sense of community and helping businesses grow through
        innovative solutions and exceptional customer service.
      </p>
      <a href="mailto:hello@localbloom.com" class="button">Contact Us</a>
    </div>

    <footer>
      <p>&copy; 2023 Metro Mesh. All rights reserved.</p>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
